&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-1261&quot; title=&quot;Replace usage of deprecated LMAX Disruptor APIs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LOG4J2-1261&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LOG4J2-1261&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; Async Loggers no longer use deprecated LMAX Disruptor APIs.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
